 r‚ÜêPush y;rc;more;space;path
‚çù Pushes the current branch
‚çù `y` must be one of:
‚çù   * Fully qualfied name of a namespace that is an opened Cider project
‚çù   * Fully qualified path to a Git-managed project
 (space path)‚ÜêEstablishProject y
 (rc more r)‚Üêpath U.RunGitCommand'push'
 more U.Assert 0=rc
‚çùDone
